{"tid":2491897,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【大家都係大陸嚟啫】香港原住民尋根之旅","createTime":"2021-04-16T15:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T15:47:40.000Z","uid":276716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab3d0e191c7d0681be1efeecd03b30555d3ab23","tid":2491897,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:41:40.000Z","msg":"全文連結：<a href=\"https://hmssulphur.blogspot.com/2021/04/blog-post.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhmssulphur.blogspot.com%2F2021%2F04%2Fblog-post.html%3Fm%3D1&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLVR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=727d84d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hmssulphur.blogspot.com/2021/04/blog-post.html?m=1</a><br />\n更多內容：<a href=\"https://mewe.com/join/scshistory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fjoin%2Fscshistory&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLVR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=2229e613\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/join/scshistory</a><br />\n<br />\n就香港原住民的族裔來源，兩位香港考古學家先後提出觀點。William Mecham認為是「泰族（Thai Ethnic Stock）」，現代粵地人口當中超過六成是其後裔，而Solomon Bard則指出可能是「大洋洲馬來裔」。兩人都認同原住民是來自海洋......"},{"pid":"f52c6c23c34c2f229b37ebb0522def173f8d04cb","tid":2491897,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6GRTMCa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6GRTMCa.png&h=33f45df5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巽他大陸的海邊和河谷可能是孕育文明的理想地點。"},{"pid":"b988af2030fc472f7ac518fa0a967cd0cbaf5ff3","tid":2491897,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SK3yMCo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSK3yMCo.jpg&h=37d8fdd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先民可能沿著巽他大陸岸邊向北遷移。"},{"pid":"efcb28cd2b4cc26d6b3e605c65ec5ce351216d62","tid":2491897,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wX01VvV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwX01VvV.jpg&h=d0a25d88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本有學者認為，繩紋人源自巽他大陸，經黑潮抵達日本列島。"},{"pid":"ad8fa4e5cde461cdc02f4a1b8687e2c81c6f1831","tid":2491897,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LRZBKps.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLRZBKps.jpg&h=bb6aeb8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高腳屋是東南亞的建築特色，可能來自巽他大陸反覆被潮水淹浸而留下的歷史記憶？"},{"pid":"4af973dc553a56b9197ffa9846500809e83f02d5","tid":2491897,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ypGDXKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FypGDXKE.jpg&h=1e6027a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紐西蘭的毛利人在節慶中舉行獨木舟競渡。他們可能是南島語族散佈得最遙遠的一支。"},{"pid":"c92f4d5d1f9a49555cd2663c0d154e5c07359f0f","tid":2491897,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2mP2EYb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2mP2EYb.jpg&h=2e08ba3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左上：香港馬灣出土的頭骨，有熱帶民族特徵，而且被拔去門牙<br />\n右上：夏威夷原住民的拔齒習俗<br />\n左下：台灣原住民邵族的拔齒習俗<br />\n右下：日本發現被拔齒的繩紋人頭骨"},{"pid":"30e8fd8920a7cc314742deb7afcaab97ea506e57","tid":2491897,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MhYffwJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhYffwJ.jpg&h=1ed802a9&s={SIZE}\" /> 這片沉沒的大陸可會是亞洲文明的真正起源？"},{"pid":"5882f97f6899437f24e7461971f233f533f24064","tid":2491897,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:47:40.000Z","msg":"參考：<br />\n<br />\n1. Oppenheimer, S. (1988) Eden in the East: the drowned Continent of Southeast Asia. Phoenix <br /